Package: nettle
Version: 1.13
Revision: 1

Description: Crypto library
DescDetail: <<
  Nettle is a cryptographic library that is designed to fit easily in
  more or less any context: In crypto toolkits for object-oriented 
  languages (C++, Python, Pike, ...), in applications like LSH or GNUPG,
  or even in kernel space.
<<

CustomMirror: <<
	Primary: http://www.lysator.liu.se/~nisse/archive/
<<

Source: mirror:custom:nettle-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 2e22612a0d7ac01064bf948a7d57f19a

BuildDepends: gmp
Depends: gmp-shlibs

SourceDirectory: nettle-%v

CompileScript: <<
	./configure --prefix=%p --infodir=%p/share/info
	make
<<

InstallScript: <<
	make install DESTDIR=%d
<<

PostInstScript: <<
	ranlib -a %p/lib/libnettle.a
<<

DescPackaging: <<
	Shared/dynamic libraries are not supported under darwin, yet.
	That's why this package does not follow the shared library packaging policy:
	http://fink.sourceforge.net/doc/packaging/policy.php?phpLang=en#sharedlibs
<<

